  "texts": [
    "Datasets are usually gathered from a variety of courses, ranging from one course to 4,699 courses, and the data collection duration differs among studies, either over every week or at the course end.",
    "Table 10 describes the datasets that are used in predicting student's academic performance including the number of students and courses used with each one of them.",
    "Waheed et al (2019 Waheed et al (, 2022)); Xie (2021); Yang and Bai (2022).",
    "• The National Tsing Hua University (NTHU) dataset, which is openly accessible, comprises data on the academic performance of NTHU undergraduate students in Taiwan captured between 2005 and 2014.",
    "The NTHU dataset contains about 1317 student's interaction behavior when watching videos and participating in laboratory sessions."
